sets/faces/pig/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n仲要妖魔化曬一切反對意見 同我講相反意見既就係弱智<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n自己中左伏都唔知 同傳銷洗腦同出一轍<br />\n<br />\nbtw 新年有無錢過年<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n你知唔知咩係SH?<br />\n係傻閪咁解呀!!!<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n人地wsb sh係SHORT HOLD 你老味就以為係STRONG HOLD<br />\n咁白痴唔呃你呃邊個<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n人地報仇關你撚事咩 你係用真金白銀呀 點同我地用信念比<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/clean.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/clean.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n好啦好啦 而家渣都無啦 舒服啦?<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"803f371f95ef2caff904ae76c57fd72c9fcbbc89","tid":2396473,"uid":125976,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-05T15:22:29.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/wVPHdaq.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FwVPHdaq.jpg&h=d06d47b4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ubZspg6.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FubZspg6.jpg&h=69b8b375&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"03